description:
On Today's Episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps all the action from Thursday nights sports slate. The Lakers are up 3-1, but do the Nuggets have them right where they want them? Can Ryan Fitzpatrick continue his strong play as the season progresses? We're joined by ESPN's Woody Paige, UCLA Head Football coach Chip Kelly, and Lakers Radio analyst Mychal Thompson
